{"about_the_game":"<i>THIS CAMPAIGN REQUIRES DCS: MI-8MTV2.</i><br><br>And again, you take over the seat of the commander of a Mi-8MTV2.<br><br>You are Dmitry Tarasov - a young pilot, who climbs the career ladder and is faced with professional difficulties that your crew helps to overcome. The adventure story of the Crew campaign consists of two parts.<br><br>In the first part, you have to perform the following tasks:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Transport of vip-passengers on the Mi-8MTV2 in the configuration &quot;Salon&quot;.<br></li><li>Work at Gazprom-Yuzhneft sites in the Krasnodar Territory.<br></li><li>Perform tasks in VFR and IFR.<br></li><li>Work on Gazprom-Arctic sites on the territory of the Bolshevik island, the Severnaya Zemlya archipelago (implemented on the Caucasus map).<br></li><li>In combat missions, you have to complete combat training flights with firing at ground targets.<br></li><li>Day and night flights.<br></li><li>To pass the Crew campaign, you will need to know about how avionics, radio and navigation equipment work. The ability to conduct sustainable helicopter control in all stages of flight is required. Skills in handling engine and instrument failures will also be useful to you.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>14 story missions<br></li><li>163 pages of detailed briefings and kneeboard<br></li><li>1320 triggers<br></li><li>1680 voiceovers</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726862544","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405240/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1726862544","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405240/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726862544","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405240/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726862544","categories":[{"description":"Single-play